description: Attention Investors and Homeowners. See this newer, bi-level, condo in boutique, 3-unit building with designer finishes, hardwood throughout, HVAC, in-unit laundry and private rear deck. This parlor/garden unit has 1,985 SF, 4+ bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms. A dramatic, large and open kitchen/living/dining room, 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms are on parlor level. The gourmet kitchen has custom cabinetry, quartz counters and stainless appliances. It has another large family room (used as 5th bedroom), 2 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms on the garden level plus additional outdoor space and ample storage. Also includes 2 nest thermostats, built-in work-from-home spaces, wet bar and wood blinds. Located in desirable City Point, near Farragut Rd and Pleasure Bay and minutes to the Seaport/Financial District and the Broadway shops and restaurants. Great investor return (6+% cap. rate) with no vacancy risk as unit is leased until 8/31/25 at monthly rent of $7,500 but with 90-day quit if necessary.
